<div class="page-header">
  <h1>
    5 Point Scotch

    <% if user_signed_in? %>
    <a href="/rounds/new" class="btn btn-lg btn-success">New Round</a>
  </h1>

     <h3>Rules and Features</h3>
     <ul>
    <li>Split into two teams.  These teams remain until the match is over.</li>
    <li>The winning team always tees off first.</li>
    <li>The losing team can decide to roll which double that hole's points after the winning team tees off.</li>
    <li>For each hole, points are awarded as follows:</li>
      <ul><li>2 points for Low Man score</li>
      <li>2 points for Low Team total</li>
      <li>1 point  for Prox (closest to the pin)</li></ul>
    <li>If a team wins Low Man, Low Team, and Prox for a hole, they win the umbrella and their points for that hole double.</li>
    <li>Each birdie doubles that team's points for that hole.</li>
    <li>Each eagle quadruples that team's points for that hole.</li>
    <ul>

